_______________________________________________________________________________
"Psychic Splice"   
        Psychic splice is a global power modifier. This allows the
        psionicist to splice powers together to perform them as a
        single action. The splice itself takes 10 spell points
        per power used inside of it, but in exchange for those sp,
        the concentration time is completely eliminated! The psionicist
        prepares the entire sequence in his mind beforehand. Powers
        within a splice will be less powerful as the Psionicist
        needs to divide his concentration among the different parts
        of the splice. The number of powers you can splice at one
        time is dependant upon your guild level.

SP Cost:  10		Guild Level:   7	Potential Points:  4
 
Command:  splice power#power#power
